---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import TopBar from "../components/TopBar";
import Hero from "../components/Hero";
import Footer from "../components/Footer";
import AboutMePicture from "../components/aboutMePicture";

import sig from '../../src/images/sig.png';
import hey from '../../src/images/hey.png';
---

<Layout title="NAKA.STUDIO | About Me">
  <main class="shadow-xl min-w-475 flex flex-1 flex-col bg-brandFloralWhite">
    <Hero />
    <TopBar />
    <section class="content h-full pt-8 px-4 text-lg">
      <a href="/" class="text-3xl p-2 border border-transparent hover:border hover:border-slate-600 transition-all rounded-sm mb-4 relative bottom-3">‚Üê</a>

      <span class="flex gap-4 text-4xl items-center mb-4"><img src={hey.src} class="w-1/2">üëã</span>

      <p class="mb-7">Welcome to my new website! My name is Alisha Nakamura and I am a hairstylist, hair educator, and mentor of over 6 years, most of which spent at an upscale salon in down Seattle, WA where I have worked for the past 6 years.</p>

      <AboutMePicture id={0} />

      <p class="mb-7">In addition to providing a wide range of hair styling services to my clients, I have also had the opportunity to train and mentor apprentices in the industry.</p>

      <p class="mb-7">
        I am passionate about being a hairstylist because I truly love making people happy. There is something special about taking care of our physical appearance that helps us feel respected and dignified, and I am dedicated to helping my clients
        achieve the look they desire.
      </p>

      <p class="mb-7">
        Growing up in Japan, where salons are a common sight on every block, has had a significant impact on my approach to styling. The Japanese place a strong emphasis on being well-groomed and presentable at all times, and this focus on perfection
        has definitely rubbed off on me as a stylist. I am not satisfied until my pursuit of technical precision leads to my clients' happiness and satisfaction.
      </p>

      <AboutMePicture id={1} />

      <p class="mb-7">
        As a hair educator and mentor, I am committed to sharing my knowledge and experience with the next generation of stylists. I believe that it is important to give back to the industry and help those who are just starting out on their own
        journey as hairstylists.
      </p>

      <p class="mb-7">
        I have a wide range of skills and experience in the beauty industry, and I am confident in my ability to provide exceptional service to every client. Thank you for considering me as your stylist, and I look forward to the opportunity to work
        with you and help you feel your best!
      </p>
      
      <img src={sig.src} alt="" class="w-3/4">
      
      <a href="/" class="text-3xl p-2 border border-transparent hover:border hover:border-slate-600 transition-all rounded-sm mb-4 relative top-3">‚Üê</a>

    </section>
  </main>
  <Footer />
</Layout>

<style>
  main {
    @apply my-0 mx-auto;
    max-width: 475px;
  }

  h1 {
    @apply text-2xl;
    font-weight: 800;
    margin: 0;
  }
</style>
